Installation
------------
- Create symbolic links:
    ln -s `pwd`/_vimrc $HOME/.vimrc
    ln -s `pwd`/_gvimrc $HOME/.gvimrc


Addon manager (optional)
------------------------
- Install the addon manager: sh InstallAddonManager.sh
- Enable the addon manager in your _vimrc by uncommenting this line:
    "call ActivateAddons
- Start Vim
- Wait while the plugins are installing.
- Done!

